Package: liu
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: libnotify-bin, fonts-noto-core
Description: Native terminal for AI-assisted coding workflows
 Liu is a native terminal built around AI-assisted ("vibe") coding workflows:
 transcript viewing and session resume across installed AI CLIs, AI-driven
 theme generation, an in-terminal file browser with a Markdown viewer, split
 panes, and prompt translate-on-tab. OpenGL/X11 renderer on Linux. No
 Electron, no JavaScript VM.
